Package annotators

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CandidateAnnotator
    Analysis engine to annotate candidates
    CandidateConsumer
    Analysis engine to save all candidates into a file
    CandidateWithVocabAnnotator
    Analysis engine to annotate candidates using a vocabulary, formatted in an rdf file with skos
    FeaturesAnnotator
    Analysis engine to annotate features in a CAS
    NGramAnnotator
    Class to compute n-grams over textual segments
    TextualSegmentAnnotator
    Analysis engine to segment a text in textual segments (basically phrases)
    Tokenizer
    Analysis engine to tokenize text, but splitting hyphen-words, over apostrophes, and ignoring numbers
    WekaClassifier
    Analysis engine to classify documents using a Weka model
    WekaModelBuilder
    An analysis engine to learn and save a Weka model
